cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper deals with character recognition using artificial neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of error backpropagation algorithm and analysis of hidden nodes also suggests that this paper may fall under machine learning (cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR) categories. Additionally, the use of MLP network indicates that this paper may also belong to neural networks (cs.NE) category.
